Hey Anon, if you come back to check, I hope you see this.<br><br>
Yes, you got to talk it, you got to face it, to get over it.<br><br>
Come on over the the other threads, pick one of the more well traveled numbers, look for the volumne, i.e. the number of posts, or even my dr. crazy corner, and post some thoughts.<br><br>
That's a lot more easy and safe than doing it in a room full of people.  Let this site do its magic. it will. You post and others answer, perhaps some e mails off site happen, but you connect, and you find out you have friends, from all sides and points of view, and you begin to slowly feel better.  <br><br>
Try it.  It sure beats the pain.<br><br>
